missionEventData.data1: What the hell! My shields just dropped.
My shields dropped agan! Looks like these rocks have some nasty tricks.
Hold it together Rogue Squadon. Evasive maneuveurs now!
Reroute energy to lasers or shields. We might not have shields but we can still out fly them.
Their defenses are too strong. Activate your rapid fire systems, maybe we'll be able to tire out their systems.
Remember once their defenses are down, to switch back to normal fire.
